high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter that is left of the stove.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the counter.
Back away from the counter.
Cut the apple that is on the counter into pieces.
Turn around, go to fridge that is ahead on the right.
Put the knife inside the fridge.
Turn to the right, go to the counter that is left of the stove.
Pick up a piece of apple from the counter.
Turn around, go to the sink that is ahead on the right.
Put the apple in the sink and rinse it off, then pick it back up.
Turn to the left and go to the fridge.
Put the apple inside the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put clean apple inside the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around, go to the stove
Pick up the knife on the counter
Turn to the edge of counter
Cut the apple on the counter
Turn around, go forward, turn right at the fridge
Put the knife in the fridge
Turn right, go to the counter
Pick up an apple piece from the counter
Turn around, go forward, turn right at the sink
Put the apple piece in the sink, wash the apple piece with water, pick up the apple piece from the sink
Turn left, go to the fridge
Put the apple piece in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Cut an apple, wash a piece of apple, cool it

high_descs: Turn around and face the stove in front of you.
Take the knife from the counter in front of you.
Look at the apple on the counter by the stove in front of you.
Slice the apple on the counter in front of you.
Turn around and face the fridge on your right.
Place the knife in the fridge in front of you and close it.
Turn right and face the stove in front of you.
Take an apple slice from the counter in front of you.
Turn around and face the sink to your right.
Wash the apple in the sink in front of you and take it out.
Turn left and face the fridge in front of you.
Place the apple in the fridge in front of you and close it.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean apple slice in the fridge.
